{"tid":1471464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請停止互相指責，馬上煲大818遊行","createTime":"2019-08-14T09:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:45:25.000Z","uid":30063,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7adedcc79b660b32a7fc745e91043f7e9ccc0a8e","tid":1471464,"uid":30063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"昨日係機場發生嘅事，可能有唔少人有意見，但唔發生都發生咗，我地由6月走到依加呢步，靠嘅就係團結一致，鬧都鬧過、屌又屌完，大家仍然係手足，目標依然係一致<br />\n<br />\n依加，有更重要嘅事，就係煲大818民陣發起嘅遊行，號召更多嘅人出嚟，100萬、200萬甚至更多，再創一次奇蹟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waNS0Yk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaNS0Yk.png&h=7769b0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P70UuRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP70UuRF.jpg&h=b6493f16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caa12ad2afcffff8eaf3eb516534ac4e304a63ae","tid":1471464,"uid":30063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21456a664bfe93d7047c41a908ac78958b0d0fb6","tid":1471464,"uid":30063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:30:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14e0cd25181638e444fb15ab22a78de98b4cca95","tid":1471464,"uid":224018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L601UjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL601UjG.jpg&h=d18bcfec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cc28614af0d0d9d53f8325aa338247183338e6a","tid":1471464,"uid":206657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b58ffb3c7cca65fb0937779add3336c7c64725f","tid":1471464,"uid":30063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /